---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Community Development - The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-8) 0;">
    <header class="reveal-on-scroll" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); text-align:center; max-width: 800px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Community Development</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
        Clinical care is only one piece of the puzzle. At The WEL Foundation, we actively invest in the socioeconomic infrastructure of Baltimore to foster environments where recovery and success can take root.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-6);">
      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-1">
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">🤝</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">Youth Mentorship</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7;">
          We pair at-risk youth with trained, culturally competent mentors who provide academic tutoring, leadership coaching, and emotional support. By intervening early, we aim to intercept behavioral health hurdles before they manifest, setting up the next generation for academic and civic triumph.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-2">
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">🍎</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">Food & Resource Security</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7;">
          Nutrition and basic physical security are foundational to mental well-being. We host monthly fresh-produce drives and operate a seasonal coat dispensary. We believe that no individual should have to choose between their clinical treatment and putting dinner on the table.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-3">
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">💼</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">Vocational Networking</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7;">
          In partnership with local Baltimore enterprises, we conduct job-readiness workshops focusing on resume building, interview etiquette, and financial literacy. We establish direct pipelines from our PRP programs into sustaining employment, restoring financial independence to our clients.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="reveal-on-scroll" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8); text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Partner With Us</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
        Are you a local business owner or community leader? Join our network to amplify our impact across Baltimore.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Reach out today</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
